title: Number sorted rows, ties have same rank
sql:
select salary, rank () over ( order by salary ) olympic_rank
from   hr.employees where department_id = 90;

    SALARY OLYMPIC_RANK
---------- ------------
     17000            1
     17000            1
     24000            3

select rank ( 20000 ) within group ( order by salary ) hypothetical_rank
from   hr.employees where department_id = 90;

HYPOTHETICAL_RANK
-----------------
                3
